hopobject.body: Have you got a current driving licence? dahlicious lassi This is just a sampling as one looks across the country of where the majority of America stands.  Have they evolved over the years on many issues?  Yes, but they also have retained some fundamental values that haven’t changed as tremendous technological, medical, cultural and industrial movement has occurred. At our core, the average American believes in fair play, accountability, honesty, compassion, responsibility and justice.
